Pundits say the race will be a proxy popularity contest between Dr Ruto and Mr Wetang’ula.
Dr Ruto has been making inroads in the area, presiding over fundraisers on the former MP’s invitation. Mr Wetang’ula’s team has got the support of Amani National Congress (ANC) party leader Musalia Mudavadi. Dr Ruto’s allies in Bungoma have are bristling for a bruising battle with Mr Wetang’ula in his backyard.
